{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 570.604,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now it came to pass that after I, Nephi, had made an end of teaching my brethren,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 6.078,
      "end": 9.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "our father, Lehi, also spake many things unto them,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 9.927,
      "end": 14.571,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and rehearsed unto them, how great things the Lord had done for them",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 14.751,
      "end": 17.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in bringing them out of the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 18.542,
      "end": 20.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spake unto them",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 20.487,
      "end": 23.273,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning their rebellions upon the waters,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 23.453,
      "end": 26.286,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the mercies of God in sparing their lives,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 26.466,
      "end": 28.881,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they were not swallowed up in the sea.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 29.561,
      "end": 33.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also spake unto them concerning the land of promise,",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 33.363,
      "end": 35.128,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which they had obtained\u2014",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 35.308,
      "end": 37.398,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how merciful the Lord had been",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 37.578,
      "end": 41.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in warning us that we should flee out of the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 42.345,
      "end": 44.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For, behold, said he,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 44.197,
      "end": 45.822,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have seen a vision,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 46.002,
      "end": 49.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in which I know that Jerusalem is destroyed;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 49.247,
      "end": 52.498,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and had we remained in Jerusalem we should also have perished.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 53.178,
      "end": 56.243,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, said he, notwithstanding our afflictions,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 56.423,
      "end": 58.791,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we have obtained a land of promise,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 58.971,
      "end": 61.943,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a land which is choice above all other lands;",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 62.123,
      "end": 65.327,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a land which the Lord God hath covenanted with me",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 65.507,
      "end": 68.618,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should be a land for the inheritance of my seed.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 68.798,
      "end": 73.814,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, the Lord hath covenanted this land unto me and to my children forever,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 73.994,
      "end": 78.824,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also all those who should be led out of other countries by the hand of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 79.504,
      "end": 82.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Lehi, prophesy",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 82.192,
      "end": 85.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the workings of the Spirit which is in me,",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 85.576,
      "end": 88.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there shall none come into this land",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 88.357,
      "end": 91.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save they shall be brought by the hand of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 91.823,
      "end": 96.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, this land is consecrated unto him whom he shall bring.",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 96.74,
      "end": 99.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if it so be that they shall serve him",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 99.428,
      "end": 102.075,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the commandments which he hath given,",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 102.255,
      "end": 104.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it shall be a land of liberty unto them;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 104.943,
      "end": 108.751,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they shall never be brought down into captivity;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 108.931,
      "end": 111.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if so, it shall be because of iniquity;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 111.851,
      "end": 114.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for if iniquity shall abound",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 114.307,
      "end": 117.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "cursed shall be the land for their sakes,",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 117.552,
      "end": 120.989,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but unto the righteous it shall be blessed forever.",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 121.669,
      "end": 123.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, it is wisdom",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 123.66,
      "end": 128.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that this land should be kept as yet from the knowledge of other nations;",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 128.53,
      "end": 132.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, many nations would overrun the land,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 132.239,
      "end": 136.465,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there would be no place for an inheritance.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 137.145,
      "end": 140.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Lehi, have obtained a promise",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 140.436,
      "end": 146.798,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that inasmuch as those whom the Lord God shall bring out of the land of Jerusalem shall keep his commandments,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 146.978,
      "end": 149.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall prosper upon the face of this land;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 150.037,
      "end": 153.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be kept from all other nations,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 153.236,
      "end": 156.022,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may possess this land unto themselves.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 156.202,
      "end": 159.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if it so be that they shall keep his commandments",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 159.772,
      "end": 162.744,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be blessed upon the face of this land,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 162.924,
      "end": 165.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there shall be none to molest them,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 165.519,
      "end": 168.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nor to take away the land of their inheritance;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 168.485,
      "end": 170.9,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall dwell safely forever.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 171.58,
      "end": 173.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, when the time cometh",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 174.082,
      "end": 176.543,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall dwindle in unbelief,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 176.723,
      "end": 180.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after they have received so great blessings from the hand of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 180.85,
      "end": 184.751,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having a knowledge of the creation of the earth, and all men,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 184.931,
      "end": 189.529,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "knowing the great and marvelous works of the Lord from the creation of the world;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 189.709,
      "end": 192.867,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having power given them to do all things by faith;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 193.047,
      "end": 195.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having all the commandments from the beginning,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 195.735,
      "end": 198.8,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and having been brought by his infinite goodness",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 198.98,
      "end": 201.163,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "into this precious land of promise\u2014",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 201.343,
      "end": 203.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, I say, if the day shall come",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 203.845,
      "end": 206.631,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they will reject the Holy One of Israel,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 206.811,
      "end": 208.065,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the true Messiah,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 208.245,
      "end": 210.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their Redeemer and their God,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 210.515,
      "end": 214.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the judgments of him that is just shall rest upon them.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 215.096,
      "end": 217.743,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, he will bring other nations unto them,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 217.923,
      "end": 219.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will give unto them power,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 220.1,
      "end": 222.376,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will take away from them",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 222.556,
      "end": 224.692,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the lands of their possessions,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 224.872,
      "end": 228.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will cause them to be scattered and smitten.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 228.896,
      "end": 233.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, as one generation passeth to another there shall be bloodsheds,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 233.256,
      "end": 235.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great visitations among them;",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 235.851,
      "end": 239.288,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, my sons, I would that ye would remember;",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 239.468,
      "end": 242.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, I would that ye would hearken unto my words.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 243.585,
      "end": 245.025,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O that ye would awake;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 245.205,
      "end": 247.063,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "awake from a deep sleep,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 247.243,
      "end": 249.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even from the sleep of hell,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 249.745,
      "end": 252.996,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shake off the awful chains by which ye are bound,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 253.176,
      "end": 257.077,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are the chains which bind the children of men,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 257.257,
      "end": 259.858,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they are carried away captive",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 260.038,
      "end": 262.917,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "down to the eternal gulf of misery and woe.",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 263.597,
      "end": 266.291,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Awake! and arise from the dust,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 266.471,
      "end": 269.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hear the words of a trembling parent,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 269.252,
      "end": 273.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose limbs ye must soon lay down in the cold and silent grave,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 273.519,
      "end": 275.887,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from whence no traveler can return;",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 276.067,
      "end": 279.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a few more days and I go the way of all the earth.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 280.602,
      "end": 283.713,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, the Lord hath redeemed my soul from hell;",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 283.893,
      "end": 285.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have beheld his glory,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 285.977,
      "end": 289.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I am encircled about eternally in the arms of his love.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 290.279,
      "end": 292.508,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I desire that ye should remember",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 292.688,
      "end": 296.125,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to observe the statutes and the judgments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 296.305,
      "end": 301.042,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, this hath been the anxiety of my soul from the beginning.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 301.722,
      "end": 305.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "My heart hath been weighed down with sorrow from time to time,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 305.431,
      "end": 307.103,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have feared,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 307.283,
      "end": 309.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest for the hardness of your hearts",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 310.157,
      "end": 312.711,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord your God should come out",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 312.891,
      "end": 315.259,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the fulness of his wrath upon you,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 315.439,
      "end": 318.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye be cut off and destroyed forever;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 318.72,
      "end": 323.828,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Or, that a cursing should come upon you for the space of many generations;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 324.008,
      "end": 327.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye are visited by sword, and by famine, and are hated,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 328.135,
      "end": 332.361,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and are led according to the will and captivity of the devil.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 333.041,
      "end": 334.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O my sons,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 334.475,
      "end": 337.029,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that these things might not come upon you,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 337.209,
      "end": 340.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but that ye might be a choice and a favored people of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 340.779,
      "end": 342.637,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, his will be done;",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 342.817,
      "end": 345.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for his ways are righteousness forever.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 346.005,
      "end": 347.584,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he hath said that:",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 347.764,
      "end": 350.504,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Inasmuch as ye shall keep my commandments",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 350.684,
      "end": 352.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall prosper in the land;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 352.722,
      "end": 355.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but inasmuch as ye will not keep my commandments",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 355.735,
      "end": 358.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall be cut off from my presence.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 358.691,
      "end": 361.199,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now that my soul might have joy in you,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 361.379,
      "end": 365.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that my heart might leave this world with gladness because of you,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 365.321,
      "end": 369.593,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I might not be brought down with grief and sorrow to the grave,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 369.773,
      "end": 372.327,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "arise from the dust, my sons, and be men,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 372.507,
      "end": 376.919,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be determined in one mind and in one heart, united in all things,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 377.099,
      "end": 379.932,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may not come down into captivity;",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 380.612,
      "end": 383.398,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "That ye may not be cursed with a sore cursing;",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 383.578,
      "end": 388.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also, that ye may not incur the displeasure of a just God upon you,",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 388.681,
      "end": 390.167,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the destruction,",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 390.347,
      "end": 393.319,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, the eternal destruction of both soul and body.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 393.999,
      "end": 395.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Awake, my sons;",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 395.712,
      "end": 397.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "put on the armor of righteousness.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 398.168,
      "end": 400.908,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Shake off the chains with which ye are bound,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 401.088,
      "end": 403.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and come forth out of obscurity,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 403.683,
      "end": 405.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and arise from the dust.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 406.081,
      "end": 408.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Rebel no more against your brother,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 408.49,
      "end": 410.719,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose views have been glorious,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 410.899,
      "end": 415.357,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who hath kept the commandments from the time that we left Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 415.537,
      "end": 418.463,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who hath been an instrument in the hands of God,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 418.643,
      "end": 421.29,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in bringing us forth into the land of promise;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 421.47,
      "end": 423.281,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for were it not for him,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 423.461,
      "end": 426.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we must have perished with hunger in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 426.752,
      "end": 429.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, ye sought to take away his life;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 429.765,
      "end": 432.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and he hath suffered much sorrow because of you.",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 433.649,
      "end": 436.528,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I exceedingly fear and tremble because of you,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 436.708,
      "end": 438.426,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest he shall suffer again;",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 438.606,
      "end": 441.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, ye have accused him",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 441.247,
      "end": 443.894,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he sought power and authority over you;",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 444.074,
      "end": 449.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but I know that he hath not sought for power nor authority over you,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 449.362,
      "end": 451.684,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but he hath sought the glory of God,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 451.864,
      "end": 453.536,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and your own eternal welfare.",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 454.216,
      "end": 457.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And ye have murmured because he hath been plain unto you.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 457.74,
      "end": 460.062,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Ye say that he hath used sharpness;",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 460.242,
      "end": 462.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye say that he hath been angry with you;",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 462.605,
      "end": 464.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold, his sharpness",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 464.596,
      "end": 468.172,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was the sharpness of the power of the word of God,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 468.352,
      "end": 469.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was in him;",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 470.065,
      "end": 473.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that which ye call anger was the truth,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 473.496,
      "end": 475.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to that which is in God,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 475.952,
      "end": 477.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he could not restrain,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 477.943,
      "end": 481.101,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "manifesting boldly concerning your iniquities.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 481.781,
      "end": 485.171,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it must needs be that the power of God must be with him,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 485.351,
      "end": 488.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even unto his commanding you that ye must obey.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 488.642,
      "end": 490.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, it was not he,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 490.772,
      "end": 493.744,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but it was the Spirit of the Lord which was in him,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 493.924,
      "end": 497.593,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which opened his mouth to utterance that he could not shut it.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 498.273,
      "end": 501.384,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now my son, Laman, and also Lemuel and Sam,",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 501.564,
      "end": 504.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my sons who are the sons of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 504.53,
      "end": 509.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, if ye will hearken unto the voice of Nephi ye shall not perish.",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 509.633,
      "end": 511.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if ye will hearken unto him",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 511.856,
      "end": 513.946,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I leave unto you a blessing,",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 514.126,
      "end": 515.891,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even my first blessing.",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 516.571,
      "end": 518.939,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But if ye will not hearken unto him",
      "verse": "1:29",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 519.119,
      "end": 521.069,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I take away my first blessing,",
      "verse": "1:29",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 521.249,
      "end": 524.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even my blessing, and it shall rest upon him.",
      "verse": "1:29",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 525.18,
      "end": 527.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, Zoram, I speak unto you:",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 527.728,
      "end": 530.282,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, thou art the servant of Laban;",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 530.462,
      "end": 534.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, thou hast been brought out of the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 535.054,
      "end": 540.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I know that thou art a true friend unto my son, Nephi, forever.",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 540.889,
      "end": 543.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, because thou hast been faithful",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 543.902,
      "end": 546.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thy seed shall be blessed with his seed,",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 546.543,
      "end": 550.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they dwell in prosperity long upon the face of this land;",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 550.81,
      "end": 554.107,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and nothing, save it shall be iniquity among them,",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 554.287,
      "end": 556.981,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall harm or disturb their prosperity",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 557.161,
      "end": 559.529,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the face of this land forever.",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 560.209,
      "end": 563.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, if ye shall keep the commandments of the Lord,",
      "verse": "1:32",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 564.151,
      "end": 568.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord hath consecrated this land for the security of thy seed",
      "verse": "1:32",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 568.371,
      "end": 569.95,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with the seed of my son.",
      "verse": "1:32",
      "lineIndex": 183
    }
  ]
}